For [example](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/48046501/create-a-java-gui-countdown-timer-that-starts-with-user-input/48046786#48046786); [example](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/33512527/java-updating-existing-stopwatch-code-to-include-countdown/33512781#33512781)

You may also want to spend some time researching the [observer pattern](https://www.google.com/search?q=java+observer+pattern), as this will provide you the means for providing feedback to interested parties about different state changing events (fyi: the `ActionListener` is an example of an observer)

