By

    if (i % 2 == 0) {
                File = &quot;FirstThread.txt&quot;;
                CurrentThread = FirstThread;
            } else {
                File = &quot;SecondThread.txt&quot;;
                CurrentThread = SecondThread;
            }

However, maybe you should consider to use ThreadName to identify your threads: [JavaDoc for Thread][1]


